---
title: Persian-Inspired Chicken Breast and Jeweled Rice with Cucumber-Yogurt Drizzle
description: Inspired by the labour-intensive dish chicken biryani, this dish has all the warm spices with the same savoury and sweet notes. Topped with spiced chicken breast and a drizzle of yogurt sauce, it's ready in a fraction of the time.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poitrines-de-poulet-et-riz-colore-a-la-perse-35f45d4e.jpg
